quran[38]{c,v,t}:
  56,1,When the Inevitable Event comes to pass
  56,2,there will be none to deny its occurrence
  56,3,it will bring some low and raise others up
  56,4,When the earth will be shaken violently
  56,5,and the mountains crushed to pieces
  56,6,and turn to scattered dust
  56,7,then you are sorted into three groups
  56,8,the people of the right – how blessed will be the people of the right
  56,9,The people of the left – how miserable will be the people of the left
  56,10,"And the forerunners [in faith] are the forerunners [in Paradise]"
  56,11,"They are the nearest ones [to Allah]"
  56,12,in Gardens of Bliss
  56,13,many from the early generations
  56,14,and a few from the later generations
  56,15,"[They will be seated] on jeweled couches"
  56,16,"reclining on them, facing one another"
  56,17,They will be served by immortal youths
  56,18,"with cups, pitchers, and glasses [of wine] from a flowing spring"
  56,19,which will neither cause any headache nor intoxication
  56,20,along with fruits of their choice
  56,21,and flesh of birds that they may desire
  56,22,"And [they will have] maidens of wide gorgeous eyes"
  56,23,like pristine pearls
  56,24,as a reward for what they used to do
  56,25,They will not hear therein any idle talk or sinful speech
  56,26,"except the words of peace, peace"
  56,27,The people of the right – how blessed will be the people of the right
  56,28,"[They will be] amid thornless lote trees"
  56,29,and clusters of bananas
  56,30,and shade long-extended
  56,31,and flowing water
  56,32,and abundant fruit –
  56,33,neither ceasing nor restricted –
  56,34,"and mattresses raised high [on beds]"
  56,35,"Indeed, We have perfectly created them [their spouses]"
  56,36,and have made them virgins
  56,37,loving and of equal age
  56,38,for the people of the right